title: Ichi Kyuu Kyuu Peke
original_name: いちきゅーきゅーぺけ
sinopse:
The manga revolves around a young man who attended a high school in a rural area, and drew his female classmates in his erotic manga. After graduating, he is accepted to a college in Tokyo. There, he finds everything he was looking for.

(Source: ANN)
